Package: modpack-updater
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, unzip
Recommends: bash-completion
Maintainer: Habier <your@email.com>
Description: Simple script to update modpack folders from a ZIP archive.
 A small utility that removes a defined set of folders from a destination
 directory and restores them from a ZIP backup. The package also installs
 an optional bash completion script and a manpage when present.
